channel.title: Enjoy my last models made for a while
channel.description:
ok these will be my last models for a while im still on vacation u know lol gona go and enjoy my family :)) so hope u enjoy these
first this is myyyyy!!!! throne room [img]http://img29.imageshack.us/img29/4421/throner.png[/img]
next is as we all know it the sushi is finally made!!!!! so chopstickz has something to eat with the chopsticks i made for him :)) [img]http://img156.imageshack.us/img156/5676/sushi6727474.png[/img]
this is my pimping sweet necklace i made [img]http://img199.imageshack.us/img199/455/neckalce.png[/img]
last i save the best for last this is my new helmet i made just for my friend it reminds me of him :)) [img]http://img199.imageshack.us/img199/3657/buket662626.png[/img]
so enjoy i love u all :)) merry Christmas to u all see you after my vacation ill stay up till bed time :)) or untill i fall asleep
